    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S is a true 'time capsule' vehicle, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a private collection. The Volcano Grey Metallic paint retains its original factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. The alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash and are wrapped in brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Inside, the Black Pebble Leather interior remains in showroom condition; the seat bolsters show no compression or wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one, and the cabin is strictly non-smoker with no odors. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized Porsche dealerships, with a meticulously documented history showing all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule. Recent service includes a comprehensive multi-point inspection, fresh oil change, and a brake fluid flush. Every electronic component, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium Bose surround sound system, functions perfectly. This is a turnkey example for a discerning buyer who demands a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
