      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example exhibits flawless mechanical synchronicity, with the double-VANOS variable valve timing system performing to factory specifications and zero evidence of rod bearing wear. The chassis is structurally pristine, having undergone a proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp-shifting Getrag 420G manual transmission to a limited-slip differential with perfect lock-up characteristics. The suspension maintains its original kinematic integrity with no bushing deflection or damper cavitation. Finished in showroom-quality paint with no orange peel or swirling, the interior is equally impressive, boasting Nappa leather with intact bolster integrity and a functional dash free of pixel degradation. A true collector-grade specimen for the driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
